<blockquote>
<p>… My only issue is that I don’t understand what the <code>double output</code> is used for in <code>useOutput()</code> method. The WPIlib example uses it for a feedforward but it’s part of the default method so I can’t change it. Does that output need to be used in a specific way?</p>
